snippet.title: Cute Suika: Big Watermelon Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Cute Suika - Big Watermelon is an adorable and fun game about dropping "fruits" into a container, with a little twist. New features and different game modes. Combine small "fruits" together to make them larger, creating big "watermelons" without overflowing the container, and enjoy the challenge.
